    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sun rooms, usually located at the back of a dwelling, equipped with a bar or other furnishings to allow preparation of beverages and entertaining of guests. Traditionally, Florida rooms have tile floors.</Note_Text>
